title: Myanmar Online Expo Park
description: Myanmar Online Expo Park, the first Virtual Online Exhibition in Myanmar, is organized by the Myanmar International Trade Center of Myanmar Trade Promotion Organization: Service Provider by Cyber King Co., Ltd as development and technical support. It is responsible for organizing, managing, and undertaking Online Trade Fair that will operate various exhibitions (including domestic exhibitions for foreign exhibitors, overseas exhibitions and domestic exhibitions), B2B Business Matching, and product advertising.
